      "raw_text": "J. P. Graves yesterday announced\nfrom New York that he had COM\npleted a deal for merging all the\nGraves electric lines under one sys-\ntenn with a backing of $4,000, 900.\nMr.. Graves also announces that he\nintends to develop water power\nnear Spokane. He is known to own\npower on the Spokane river and\nthis Is probably what is referred to."
